109
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:05,960
So I thought she must've left.

110
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:09,200
That's why I went home.

111
00:10:10,519 --> 00:10:11,440
That's it.

112
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:18,500
