154
00:12:53,159 --> 00:12:54,679
and why I can't remember anything.

155
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:55,680
So what?

156
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:57,080
I don't remember anything either.

157
00:12:57,300 --> 00:12:58,390
Then isn't that exactly

158
00:12:58,399 --> 00:13:00,039
why we need to find out now?

159
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:02,759
