164
00:13:13,399 --> 00:13:14,840
we start twisting the facts

165
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:16,000
to fit our theories.

166
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,000
And that's wrong.

167
00:13:18,879 --> 00:13:20,399
So if you're not mentally prepared

168
00:13:20,399 --> 00:13:23,080
to face the worst possible outcome,

169
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,920
then we might as well
stop investigating now.

170
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,790
And what could be
the worst possible outcome?

171
00:13:29,919 --> 00:13:30,480
What...

172
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,639
What's the matter?

173
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:44,919
Are you okay?

174
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:00,519
My son,

175
