182
00:14:22,799 --> 00:14:23,600
No?

183
00:14:24,879 --> 00:14:26,679
Then you must have had a crush on her.

184
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,200
No, there's nothing between us.

185
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:32,680
No relationship at all.

186
00:14:44,559 --> 00:14:45,960
