194
00:15:08,159 --> 00:15:10,000
there's no point at all.

195
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:12,120
Do you understand?

196
00:15:14,879 --> 00:15:16,279
Are you really going

197
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:18,440
to risk your life over this?

198
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:21,279
