199
00:15:26,279 --> 00:15:28,000
Don't even try to reason with me.

200
00:15:28,140 --> 00:15:29,000
I don't understand,

201
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:30,200
and I don't want to listen it.

202
00:15:30,879 --> 00:15:32,759
Truth, justice,

203
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:35,320
or whatever.

204
00:15:35,679 --> 00:15:36,480
I don't get all that

205
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:37,639
and I don't care.

206
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:44,000
All I want is for our family

207
00:15:44,240 --> 00:15:45,440
to be happy

208
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:48,840
and live our lives in peace.

209
00:15:55,879 --> 00:15:57,600
Do you hear me?

210
00:16:01,919 --> 00:16:02,720
All right, I'll stop.

211
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:05,269
Get up and have some fruit

212
00:16:05,270 --> 00:16:06,400
to replenish vitamin C.

213
00:16:06,559 --> 00:16:07,399
