to the leather.

257
00:20:04,079 --> 00:20:05,599
Siyuan, he has a gun.

258
00:20:05,620 --> 00:20:07,900
Besides destroying the evidence,
he wants to kill you too.

259
00:20:07,900 --> 00:20:09,200
Do your mom and sister know

260
00:20:11,279 --> 00:20:12,440
you're here?

261
00:20:15,319 --> 00:20:16,079
No.

262
00:20:18,839 --> 00:20:20,799
But the 300 viewers
in my livestream do.

263
00:20:23,200 --> 00:20:24,420
There are 350 viewers now.

264
00:20:27,580 --> 00:20:29,880
(A university student takes you
into the home of a deranged killer!)

265
00:20:33,599 --> 00:20:34,839
This is an act of defamation.

266
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:36,960
I'm not even a suspect.

267
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:38,079
