277
00:20:56,840 --> 00:20:58,420
I'll give you guys a boost tomorrow.

278
00:20:58,480 --> 00:20:59,750
Has anyone ever told you

279
00:21:01,279 --> 00:21:03,200
that you and your brother look alike?

280
00:21:09,319 --> 00:21:10,000
Too bad.

281
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,519
If my brother were still alive,

282
00:21:13,359 --> 00:21:16,079
