286
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:42,920
Xun.

287
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:45,280
It's been a long time.

288
00:22:46,319 --> 00:22:47,920
Who told you to activate this phone?

289
00:22:48,680 --> 00:22:51,680
Things are getting complicated
on my end.

290
00:22:54,839 --> 00:22:56,160
The cops are onto me.

291
00:22:56,920 --> 00:22:57,839
You have to help me.

292
00:22:58,319 --> 00:23:00,160
Why does that concern me?

293
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:01,279
Bye.

294
00:23:01,279 --> 00:23:02,160
Xun, wait.

295
00:23:03,119 --> 00:23:04,079
Don't hang up, Xun.

296
00:23:05,559 --> 00:23:07,119
This isn't just about me.

297
00:23:07,799 --> 00:23:08,799
Also, I suspect...

298
00:23:11,920 --> 00:23:13,440
I suspect Liao Siyuan knows.

299
00:23:17,039 --> 00:23:17,799
Stay on the line.

300
00:23:25,799 --> 00:23:26,400
Boss,

301
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:27,599
Song En called.

302
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:29,480
(Liu Haixun)
He mentioned Liao Siyuan.

303
00:23:30,780 --> 00:23:32,720
After all these years of keeping
that bait,

304
00:23:32,839 --> 00:23:34,759
it looks like it's finally useful.

305
00:23:34,880 --> 00:23:36,830
What could a university student
possibly know?

306
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:39,519
Draw out the one
who should've died a long time ago.

307
00:23:40,279 --> 00:23:40,920
Yes, Boss.

308
00:23:41,799 --> 00:23:43,599
Song En, listen to me.

309
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:45,200
From now on,

310
00:23:45,559 --> 00:23:47,480
do what I instruct you.

311
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:48,440
Got it?

312
00:23:54,799 --> 00:23:56,160
You're using me as bait

313
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:57,279
to lure someone out.

314
00:23:58,559 --> 00:23:59,839
I could die here.

315
00:24:00,599 --> 00:24:02,240
Do you think not following orders

316
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:03,359
will keep you alive?

317
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:04,720
Don't forget.

318
00:24:04,920 --> 00:24:06,240
I could protect you ten years ago.

319
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:07,760
I can do the same again today.

320
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,200
Just do as I say.

321
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:38,680
This is Cai...
Cai Na's ex-boyfriend, Mike.

322
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:40,799
I know a bit about Lai La's situation.

323
00:24:41,680 --> 00:24:44,160
I will answer everything you ask.

324
00:24:46,359 --> 00:24:47,279
I want to know

325
00:24:49,079 --> 00:24:51,319
why Cai Na jumped to her death.

326
00:24:52,359 --> 00:24:53,759
I'm not too sure about this.

327
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:56,780
But it certainly had nothing
to do with our relationship.

328
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,880
Why did you two break up?

329
00:25:07,240 --> 00:25:09,000
At first,

330
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:11,680
my relationship
with Cai Na was very stable.

331
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:13,559
But there was a time

332
00:25:13,760 --> 00:25:15,880
when Cai Na and Lai La spent
a lot of time together.

333
00:25:16,599 --> 00:25:18,799
After that, Cai Na suddenly
became desperate for money.

334
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:21,279
She even borrowed a lot from me.

335
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:24,680
I couldn't take it anymore

336
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,720
so I broke up with her.

337
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:28,680
I have one more question.

338
00:25:29,119 --> 00:25:31,039
Do you know where Cai Na lived?

339
00:25:43,240 --> 00:25:44,039
Please come in.

340
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:49,039
This is Cai Na's room.

341
00:25:50,119 --> 00:25:51,119
After she died,

342
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:55,000
none of the arrangements
in this room were changed.

343
00:25:57,640 --> 00:26:00,400
I come in to clean every day.

344
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:03,400
Seeing these things

345
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:06,960
makes me feel like Cai Na

346
00:26:08,039 --> 00:26:08,960
is still alive.

347
00:26:13,839 --> 00:26:14,680
This bed...

348
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,200
This is Lai La's bed.

349
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:21,519
She and Lai La became really close
in high school.

350
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:26,000
Later, when Lai La ran away from home
to escape an arranged marriage,

351
00:26:27,000 --> 00:26:29,160
she stayed here for a long time.

352
00:26:33,080 --> 00:26:35,740
She ran away from an arranged marriage
during high school?

353
00:26:37,079 --> 00:26:37,759
Yes.

354
00:26:39,079 --> 00:26:40,240
She was still a child.

355
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,680
I can still remember

356
00:26:44,400 --> 00:26:47,880
what she looked like that day.

357
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:57,200
Cai Na!

358
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:00,880
Cai Na!

359
00:27:02,000 --> 00:27:02,720
Cai Na!

360
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:14,000
I thought you went home.

361
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:16,160
Why are you...

362
00:27:17,880 --> 00:27:19,240
I have no home to go back to.

363
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:27,799
- Lai La!
- Let me go!

364
00:27:27,799 --> 00:27:28,319
Lai La!

365
00:27:28,319 --> 00:27:28,920
Come here!

366
00:27:29,039 --> 00:27:30,400
Lai La. Lai La.

367
00:27:30,640 --> 00:27:32,359
Be good and get changed.

368
00:27:32,359 --> 00:27:33,839
The groom's family will be here soon.

369
00:27:33,839 --> 00:27:34,519
No!

370
00:27:35,799 --> 00:27:36,599
Hey!

371
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:38,319
What are you doing?

372
00:27:41,599 --> 00:27:42,799
I still want to go to school.

373
00:27:42,880 --> 00:27:44,319
What's the point of studying?

374
00:27:46,920 --> 00:27:47,720
Lai La,

375
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,680
you were born here.

376
00:27:49,880 --> 00:27:52,039
So you have to follow the rules here.

377
00:27:53,200 --> 00:27:54,599
The women in our town get married

378
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:57,440
when the time comes.

379
00:27:58,200 --> 00:28:00,279
Lai La, be good.

380
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:01,559
Put that down.

381
00:28:01,839 --> 00:28:02,920
Don't do anything foolish.

382
00:28:07,359 --> 00:28:07,920
Lai La.

383
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:10,319
I would rather die than come back!

384
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:12,079
Don't do it, Lai La!

385
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,000
Come in.

386
00:28:58,680 --> 00:28:59,400
Come here.

387
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:01,799
We'll buy a new bed tomorrow

388
00:29:01,799 --> 00:29:02,599
and place it there.

389
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:05,039
You can stay as long as you want.

390
00:29:05,599 --> 00:29:07,559
This will be your home from now on.

391
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:11,300
But wouldn't it be too much trouble
for you?

392
00:29:12,000 --> 00:29:13,000
Of course not.

393
00:29:14,799 --> 00:29:15,559
Thank you.

394
00:29:16,640 --> 00:29:17,359
Don't mention it.

395
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:18,839
Come on, cheer up.

396
00:29:18,839 --> 00:29:20,200
Put on a smile.

397
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:26,680
Hello, Lai La.

398
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,240
The streetlights here are broken.

399
00:29:28,400 --> 00:29:29,839
Can you come and get me?

400
00:29:43,480 --> 00:29:44,920
What's in your bag?

401
00:29:45,119 --> 00:29:45,759
Weapon.

402
00:29:58,319 --> 00:29:59,839
She never talked

403
00:30:01,799 --> 00:30:03,079
about her family.

404
00:30:03,079 --> 00:30:04,440
We never asked either.

405
00:30:06,079 --> 00:30:07,440
But a few days ago,

406
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:09,880
I ran into Lai La's parents by chance

407
00:30:10,599 --> 00:30:13,000
when I went to school
to pack up Cai Na's things.

408
00:30:13,279 --> 00:30:16,920
That's when I found out the kind of life

409
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:21,039
she had been living for over ten years.

410
00:30:24,359 --> 00:30:25,880
That poor child.

411
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,720
She came into this world

412
00:30:29,519 --> 00:30:30,960
only to suffer.

413
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,599
Lai La is now gone.

414
00:30:41,440 --> 00:30:43,440
These are the few belongings she left,

415
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:46,440
with no one to even sort them out.

416
00:30:48,640 --> 00:30:50,200
After what happened to Lai La,

417
00:30:50,200 --> 00:30:52,680
we also suspected
that Cai Na didn't take her own life.

418
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:57,200
But we don't have the means
to investigate.

419
00:31:00,559 --> 00:31:02,119
So I'll leave this information to you.

420
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:13,320
(Cai Na's egg retrieval
and tube removal records.)

421
00:31:14,279 --> 00:31:14,759
Mrs...

422
00:31:14,759 --> 00:31:16,359
I know what you want to ask.

423
00:31:18,319 --> 00:31:21,119
We may not be rich.

424
00:31:21,119 --> 00:31:21,920
But

425
00:31:23,559 --> 00:31:24,400
we never

426
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:28,640
let Cai Na worry about money.

427
00:31:30,319 --> 00:31:31,319
I don't even know

428
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:35,440
why she did something so foolish.

429
00:31:39,559 --> 00:31:41,519
She could have told me about everything.

430
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:07,359
Siyuan,

431
00:32:08,359 --> 00:32:10,359
do you remember
the records of those girls

432
00:32:10,359 --> 00:32:12,039
we found at Song En's clinic?

433
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:14,599
At first, I thought

434
00:32:14,799 --> 00:32:16,079
they were linked to prostitution.

435
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:19,960
So that was a catalog?

436
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:24,319
If Cai Na was selling her eggs,

437
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:26,160
then Lai La's unborn child could be...

438
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,220
A surrogate pregnancy.

439
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:31,279
Song En runs a clinic on the surface.

440
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:33,279
But behind the scenes,

441
00:32:33,280 --> 00:32:36,160
he's illegally exploiting young girls
for egg harvesting and surrogacy.

442
00:32:36,740 --> 00:32:37,790
This might be connected

443
00:32:37,799 --> 00:32:39,200
to Lai La and Cai Na's deaths.

444
00:32:39,940 --> 00:32:42,100
We need to report this
to the police immediately.

445
00:32:42,119 --> 00:32:43,400
I'll call my sister now.

446
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:52,759
The results are in.

447
00:32:53,119 --> 00:32:54,079
Lai La and the baby

448
00:32:54,079 --> 00:32:55,200
have no biological relation.

449
00:32:56,320 --> 00:32:57,480
So it really was surrogacy?

450
00:32:59,079 --> 00:33:00,400
It looks like Siyuan was right.

451
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:02,799
We need to arrest Song En
as soon as possible

452
00:33:02,960 --> 00:33:05,599
before more girls get hurt.

453
00:33:16,520 --> 00:33:17,420
I want you guys

454
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:20,119
to gather the files
on every missing woman in Buhe.

455
00:33:20,599 --> 00:33:21,829
Track every financial

456
00:33:21,830 --> 00:33:23,100
transaction linked to Song En.

457
00:33:23,540 --> 00:33:25,160
I'll request a warrant for his arrest.

458
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:26,079
Be on standby.

459
00:33:26,079 --> 00:33:27,240
Ready to move at any time.

460
00:33:27,240 --> 00:33:28,420
- Yes, sir!
- Yes, sir!

461
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:13,710
Split up, cover both stairways
and head up.

462
00:34:14,119 --> 00:34:14,639
Move out.

463
00:34:14,639 --> 00:34:15,159
Yes, sir.

464
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:16,840
Break the door down!

465
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:18,239
Break it down now! Break it!

466
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,119
Chief.

467
00:35:20,719 --> 00:35:21,400
Chief!

468
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:38,159
Chief!

469
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:40,599
Give that to me!

470
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:45,880
Break this door!

471
00:37:05,679 --> 00:37:06,480
Chief!

472
00:37:07,639 --> 00:37:08,199
Freeze!

473
00:37:08,519 --> 00:37:09,079
Police!

474
00:37:11,559 --> 00:37:12,360
Chief.

475
00:37:14,679 --> 00:37:15,519
Where's Song En?

476
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:18,000
He's out to kill Liao Siyuan.

477
00:37:34,627 --> 00:37:39,065
♪The night stretches long,
like an endless hallway♪

478
00:37:40,427 --> 00:37:45,584
♪Without moonlight
or a god to guide the way♪

479
00:37:46,221 --> 00:37:51,092
♪Memories drip
within the center of my heart♪

480
00:37:51,347 --> 00:37:56,111
♪Burning you away,
leaving only emptiness♪

481
00:37:56,318 --> 00:37:59,130
♪The distorted truth♪

482
00:37:59,308 --> 00:38:04,893
♪Is tampered with,
buried, and forgotten♪

483
00:38:07,542 --> 00:38:13,456
♪Beyond the embers,
the wound remains warm♪

484
00:38:13,622 --> 00:38:18,407
♪It lights up again♪

485
00:38:19,136 --> 00:38:24,769
♪Whose hands♪

486
00:38:25,024 --> 00:38:28,348
♪Are pulling the strings?♪

487
00:38:28,505 --> 00:38:30,932
♪Who stands at the end of the lie?♪

488
00:38:30,941 --> 00:38:36,422
♪Behind the mask♪

489
00:38:36,775 --> 00:38:40,055
♪Whose softness♪

490
00:38:40,345 --> 00:38:42,167
♪Has decayed?♪

491
00:38:42,267 --> 00:38:45,975
♪Lift the dust, feel it with your soul♪

492
00:38:45,977 --> 00:38:50,902
♪The chains of destiny
have long bound us♪

493
00:38:51,147 --> 00:38:53,907
♪To each other♪

494
00:38:54,381 --> 00:38:56,846
♪If you don't die, I won't stop♪

495
00:38:56,914 --> 00:38:59,693
♪Let's witness together♪

496
00:38:59,797 --> 00:39:02,976
♪The end♪
